author: Staff
title: Midcoast Track and Field Stars Shine Bright in Jan. 15 Meet
text:
BRUNSWICK — William Farley Field House at Bowdoin College has been, essentially, the home base for all track teams throughout the Kennebec Valley Athletic Conference all season.
That trend continued Wednesday, Jan. 15 in a nine-team meet, which included student-athletes from Belfast, Oceanside, Camden Hills and Medomak Valley all sprinting, throwing and leaping their way to impressive individual performances.
